<li>
<p>Open javaProject &lt; src &lt; main &lt; java\com.. &lt; service &lt; de=
moapplication.java &lt; <strong>Run&nbsp;</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<p></p>
<p>These are the following API=E2=80=99s developed and their actions:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Post API=E2=80=99s :&nbsp;</p></li>
</ol>
