<li>
<p>First an admin should sign up.</p></li>
<li>
<p>If the admin is already in the database, the admin can directly sign in.=
&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>After the signing process a token is generated so that token is used as =
the authentication, using that generated token while signing in, the admin =
can add a new person and employee details at same time to different tables =
with Post api.</p></li>
<li>
<p>And next, using get api admin can retrieve the information of the person=
al details and employee details.&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>&nbsp;And finally the admin can update the details of any employee using=
 the put api.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Authenticating bearer tokens should be used to access any of the service=
s.&nbsp;</p></li>
</ol>
